description.en: Carbon is a free and open-source web browser developed by Carbon X Labs based on a custom fork of the Chromium SDK and its powerful Blink engine. Carbon is a fast privacy-focused browser, which blocks online ads and trackers.  Currently live on Google Play Store and coming soon to iOS, Mac OS and PC.
